  "title": "45.5 (LOA)",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Do you remember how I spoke of this presence I\u2019ve felt during our meeting with Elder Thrush\u2014the stirring unease of some undefinable presence within the arcology? I\u2019ve been attempting to reach it to no avail."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cI think, however, that I may have a solution: Greenbriar Knoll. It is a place of great power. Were we to go there, I should be able to harness that power and, with the help of the spirits, use it to penetrate whatever barrier stands between me and the elusive presence."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cDo you have time to accompany me to Greenbriar Knoll? I would certainly appreciate the company.\u201d"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Rangers Choose"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "link": {
            "id": null,
            "anchor": "rangers-choose",
            "url": "#rangers-choose"
          }
        }
      ],
      "anchor": "rangers-choose"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "span",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A) You can count on me."
                }
              ],
              "color": "red"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Discard all"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "icon",
              "icon": "progress",
              "color": "black"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "and attach the"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "HELPING HAND"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "mission to Spirit Speaker Nal. Accompany Nal to Greenbriar Knoll."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "span",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "B) Sorry, Nal. Greenbriar Knoll gives me the creeps."
                }
              ],
              "color": "red"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Discard Spirit Speaker Nal. Each Ranger soothes 2 fatigue."
        }
      ]
    }
